sqlite3 "/Users/david/workspace/claude-code-claimdb/test_dbs/financial.sqlite" "
-- Check distinct clients with accounts in Prague (account district)
SELECT 
  COUNT(DISTINCT c.client_id) as total,
  COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN c.gender = 'F' THEN c.client_id END) as female_count,
  CAST(COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN c.gender = 'F' THEN c.client_id END) AS REAL) / COUNT(DISTINCT c.client_id) * 100 as female_pct
FROM client c
JOIN disp d ON c.client_id = d.client_id
JOIN account a ON d.account_id = a.account_id
JOIN district dist ON a.district_id = dist.district_id
WHERE dist.A3 = 'Prague';
"
